{"tid":925673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【賣畀對手】三星供應商被起訴　涉向華為供應商出售曲面屏幕技術","createTime":"2018-12-03T02:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T02:24:33.000Z","uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"67b5a03e4a6cda2c25f6ea5a05ad70b90b5ab90e","tid":925673,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:15:57.000Z","msg":"全球最大手機製造商三星（Samsung）的手機技術遭竊，三星供應商TOPTEC涉嫌「賣國」，將三星招牌「OLED曲面螢幕」技術出售予其對手中國手機製商，南韓檢方已起訴11名員工。<br />\n<br />\n傳買方為京東方科技集團<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報道，涉案的TOPTEC行政總裁及8名員工涉嫌收取155億韓圜（約1.08億港元）轉賣技術。他們成立一間空殼公司，獲取三星技術草圖與其他設備後，再轉售予中國面板廠，涉案人使用虛假姓名、聯繫方式及個人郵箱地址加以掩飾。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，TOPTEC由於今年銷情不佳，主動向中國企業提議轉讓技術。消息人士亦指，買方為三星對手華為的主要供應商&mdash;&mdash;京東方科技集團，現時華為是僅次於三星的全球最大手機製造商，明年兩間公司將共同發布可折疊手機。<br />\n<br />\n洩曲面OLED料損58億美元銷售額<br />\n<br />\n南韓檢方提到，遭洩漏的曲面OLED技術是三星研發6年的成果，期內共投資1,500億韓圜（約10.5億港元），更被指定為《南韓工業技術保護法》所保障的「國家核心技術」。該技術是三星手機的獨家招牌，現應用於Galaxy Note 9之中。<br />\n<br />\n據報，三星發言人對這項起訴表示遺憾，強調會加倍努力保護技術資料，並預計技術外洩將令公司在未來3年損失約58億美元銷售額，以及8.9億美元的利潤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/265857/%E8%B3%A3%E7%95%80%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B-%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%95%86%E8%A2%AB%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4-%E6%B6%89%E5%90%91%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%95%86%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E6%9B%B2%E9%9D%A2%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F265857%2F%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E7%2595%2580%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2589%258B-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2598%259F%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2594%25AE%25E6%259B%25B2%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25B1%258F%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593&d=j2VufJ7sHyWA%2BEuaD8bPObIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=3daf67ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/265857/%E8%B3%A3%E7%95%80%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B-%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%95%86%E8%A2%AB%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4-%E6%B6%89%E5%90%91%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%95%86%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E6%9B%B2%E9%9D%A2%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93</a>"},{"pid":"7ce78d10e43ece7c6d7b6bd6861ae3cdd8a80e7e","tid":925673,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:17:54.000Z","msg":"TOPTEC由於今年銷情不佳，主動向中國企業提議轉讓技術。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搵食啫"},{"pid":"3ebe4842718ee889dad3e3401aa015b148860abc","tid":925673,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:19:08.000Z","msg":"唔偷唔搶邊可能咁快領先到"},{"pid":"59e53ec6b31c6a36e4ffe9b23fc822ac6eb35e58","tid":925673,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fa0cfd45baa6d94a09498597c20c70ea46ac56","tid":925673,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"得罪3叔你在個行頭仲洗搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11debec9f25898d6b2645fd278ed000906a172d8","tid":925673,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87fa0cfd45baa6d94a09498597c20c70ea46ac56","tid":925673,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"得罪3叔你在個行頭仲洗搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:24:33.000Z","msg":"靠中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你偷用野 無利用價值 仲會比生意你做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}